metadata.name: Juniper 2
metadata.description:
One of my favourite drawings Juniper 2 stands strong and elegant surrounded by the elements. The curvature of the trunk and patterns of the foliage forge to give a sense of calm. 

Over a hundred hours spent traditionally drawn pen and ink dark art piece.
